{
  "video_id": "f5NJQiY9AuY",
  "title": "Bill Gates Chats with Ellen for the First Time",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 300.0,
      "end_time": 1780.0,
      "text": "I am so happy to have you here."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1780.0,
      "end_time": 4380.0,
      "text": "This is the first time having you on, so thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4380.0,
      "end_time": 7200.0,
      "text": "So I know you were nervous about the entrance."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7200.0,
      "end_time": 9209.0,
      "text": "I think people feel like they're supposed to dance."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 11460.0,
      "end_time": 12960.0,
      "text": "And I was really surprised because I"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12960.0,
      "end_time": 15450.0,
      "text": "was here earlier today for your rehearsal"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 15450.0,
      "end_time": 16830.0,
      "text": "and then you abandoned it."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 16830.0,
      "end_time": 18930.0,
      "text": "But we should at least show them the rehearsal"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 18930.0,
      "end_time": 20881.0,
      "text": "because it was really good."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 20882.0,
      "end_time": 23820.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 23820.0,
      "end_time": 25552.0,
      "text": "[LAUGHING]"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 25552.0,
      "end_time": 28516.0,
      "text": "[CHEERING]"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43830.0,
      "end_time": 44818.0,
      "text": "It was good."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44818.0,
      "end_time": 50410.0,
      "text": "[APPLAUSE]"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50410.0,
      "end_time": 52400.0,
      "text": "Your daughter is looking at you like, I've never"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52400.0,
      "end_time": 54839.0,
      "text": "seen you dance like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54840.0,
      "end_time": 56000.0,
      "text": "Hi."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56000.0,
      "end_time": 57707.0,
      "text": "So the last time we saw each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57707.0,
      "end_time": 58790.0,
      "text": "it was at the White House."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58790.0,
      "end_time": 61519.0,
      "text": "We both were receiving the Medal of Freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61520.0,
      "end_time": 63200.0,
      "text": "And that was quite a day, wasn't it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63200.0,
      "end_time": 64103.0,
      "text": "That was an amazing group."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64102.00000000001,
      "end_time": 64610.00000000001,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 64610.0,
      "end_time": 66500.0,
      "text": "Really, really fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 66500.0,
      "end_time": 70900.0,
      "text": "So you are here with your daughter who is 21, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 70100.0,
      "end_time": 73220.0,
      "text": "And you were 21 when you became a billionaire."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 73220.0,
      "end_time": 74480.0,
      "text": "Is that right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 74480.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "Almost, yep."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 76910.0,
      "text": "All right, so around that age."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 76910.0,
      "end_time": 79880.0,
      "text": "You were like the youngest person to become a billionaire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 79880.0,
      "end_time": 81789.0,
      "text": "is that right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 81790.0,
      "end_time": 84320.0,
      "text": "Yeah, in terms of earning it on my own, yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 84320.0,
      "end_time": 84830.0,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 84830.0,
      "end_time": 85550.0,
      "text": "OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 85550.0,
      "end_time": 87670.0,
      "text": "Which is the most important thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 87670.0,
      "end_time": 92150.0,
      "text": "So when you were a kid, did you care about money?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 92150.0,
      "end_time": 93920.0,
      "text": "Or you just cared about technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 93920.0,
      "end_time": 96200.0,
      "text": "and it just happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 96200.0,
      "end_time": 98300.0,
      "text": "Mostly I loved software."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 98300.0,
      "end_time": 99860.0,
      "text": "I do remember at the private school"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 99860.0,
      "end_time": 103700.0,
      "text": "I went to there were other kids whose families were better off."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 103700.0,
      "end_time": 104669.0,
      "text": "Like they had a Porsche or something."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 104670.0,
      "end_time": 107300.0,
      "text": "But it wasn't that big of a deal"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 107300.0,
      "end_time": 109670.0,
      "text": "My thing was that I just loved doing software."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 109670.0,
      "end_time": 111380.0,
      "text": "I loved hiring people."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 111380.0,
      "end_time": 114740.0,
      "text": "And I was stunned when it ended up being so valuable."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 114740.0,
      "end_time": 115369.0,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 115370.0,
      "end_time": 116330.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 116330.0,
      "end_time": 117620.0,
      "text": "It surprised you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 117620.0,
      "end_time": 118430.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 118430.0,
      "end_time": 121240.0,
      "text": "Because I always had to be careful that we"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 121240.0,
      "end_time": 122490.0,
      "text": "wouldn't hire too many people."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 122490.0,
      "end_time": 124298.0,
      "text": "I was always worried because people"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 124299.0,
      "end_time": 126590.0,
      "text": "who worked for me were older than me and they had kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 126590.0,
      "end_time": 128942.0,
      "text": "And I always thought well what if we don't get paid."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 128942.0,
      "end_time": 130400.0,
      "text": "Will I be able to meet the payroll?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 130400.0,
      "end_time": 132800.0,
      "text": "So I was always very conservative"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 132800.0,
      "end_time": 134300.0,
      "text": "about the finances."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 134300.0,
      "end_time": 140150.0,
      "text": "And then when we did go public, what was I?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 140150.0,
      "end_time": 142550.0,
      "text": "30, by then."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 142550.0,
      "end_time": 145700.0,
      "text": "Then I was kind of stunned at what it multiplied out to."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 145700.0,
      "end_time": 146239.0,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 146240.0,
      "end_time": 148430.0,
      "text": "So, when you became a billionaire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 148430.0,
      "end_time": 150602.0,
      "text": "at what point did you start relaxing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 150602.0,
      "end_time": 152810.0,
      "text": "Were you still nervous when you became a billionaire?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 152810.0,
      "end_time": 155180.0,
      "text": "Like I got to watch this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 155180.0,
      "end_time": 157950.0,
      "text": "Well I always wanted to have enough money in the bank"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 157950.0,
      "end_time": 160730.0,
      "text": "so that even if our customers didn't pay us for a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 160730.0,
      "end_time": 163959.0,
      "text": "we could still keep paying everybody and do the R&D."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 163960.0,
      "end_time": 168320.0,
      "text": "So I'd still be viewed as conservative."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 168320.0,
      "end_time": 171600.0,
      "text": "I don't have that many things that are extravagant taste"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 171600.0,
      "end_time": 174227.0,
      "text": "so it didn't change too much."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 174227.0,
      "end_time": 175310.0,
      "text": "So nothing really changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 175310.0,
      "end_time": 177721.0,
      "text": "So you didn't say, oh I'm going to buy a Porsche."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 177721.0,
      "end_time": 178220.0,
      "text": "I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 178220.0,
      "end_time": 178510.0,
      "text": "That I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 178510.0,
      "end_time": 178959.0,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 178960.0,
      "end_time": 179435.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 179435.0,
      "end_time": 179935.0,
      "text": "You did."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 179935.0,
      "end_time": 180460.0,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 180460.0,
      "end_time": 182810.0,
      "text": "Yeah, that was an indulgence."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 182810.0,
      "end_time": 186500.0,
      "text": "And then eventually, for my travel, I got a plane."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 186500.0,
      "end_time": 188160.0,
      "text": "Which is a huge indulgence."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 188160.0,
      "end_time": 189450.0,
      "text": "So those are my two."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 189450.0,
      "end_time": 191730.0,
      "text": "Well not really, because you travel all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 191730.0,
      "end_time": 193730.0,
      "text": "So that's important that you have a plane."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 193730.0,
      "end_time": 196890.0,
      "text": "So you have a Porsche and a plane and that's it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 196890.0,
      "end_time": 198940.0,
      "text": "Well, in terms of crazy things, yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 198941.0,
      "end_time": 199440.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 199440.0,
      "end_time": 201372.0,
      "text": "There's not like any like wild-- like you"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 201372.0,
      "end_time": 203330.0,
      "text": "didn't build like an aquarium with sharks in it"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 203330.0,
      "end_time": 204760.0,
      "text": "or something like that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 204760.0,
      "end_time": 206476.0,
      "text": "We have a trampoline room in our house."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 206476.0,
      "end_time": 206975.0,
      "text": "Oh wow."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 206975.0,
      "end_time": 207920.0,
      "text": "The kids like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 207920.0,
      "end_time": 209119.0,
      "text": "Indoor trampoline."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 209120.0,
      "end_time": 212000.0,
      "text": "I recommend it."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 212000.0,
      "end_time": 213680.0,
      "text": "Just one giant trampoline?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 213680.0,
      "end_time": 214390.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 214390.0,
      "end_time": 216750.0,
      "text": "Yeah, it's a room with a very high ceiling."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 216750.0,
      "end_time": 218300.0,
      "text": "Well yeah, I hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 218300.0,
      "end_time": 219950.0,
      "text": "That would be cruel if you didn't"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 219950.0,
      "end_time": 221980.0,
      "text": "put a high ceiling in there."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 221980.0,
      "end_time": 224241.0,
      "text": "Go on kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 224241.0,
      "end_time": 225740.0,
      "text": "All right, so let's talk about this."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 225740.0,
      "end_time": 230780.0,
      "text": "So you already put $40 billion of your own money"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 230780.0,
      "end_time": 232230.0,
      "text": "into your foundation."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 232230.0,
      "end_time": 232730.0,
      "text": "Yep."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 232730.0,
      "end_time": 233670.0,
      "text": "$40 billion."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 233670.0,
      "end_time": 237739.0,
      "text": "And you've kind of encouraged other billionaires"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 237740.0,
      "end_time": 239300.0,
      "text": "to do this as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 239300.0,
      "end_time": 241970.0,
      "text": "Because it really is kind of up to the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 241970.0,
      "end_time": 245570.0,
      "text": "to fix the problems in the world, it seems, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 245570.0,
      "end_time": 249769.0,
      "text": "So what is your main focus right now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 249770.0,
      "end_time": 253220.0,
      "text": "My wife Melinda and I picked global health as our big thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 253220.0,
      "end_time": 256370.0,
      "text": "The fact that still we have five million kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 256370.0,
      "end_time": 258709.0,
      "text": "who die under the age of five."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 258709.0,
      "end_time": 260180.0,
      "text": "Now it was over 10 million when we"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 260180.0,
      "end_time": 264320.0,
      "text": "got started so there's been huge progress over the last 18"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 264320.0,
      "end_time": 265920.0,
      "text": "years."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 265920.0,
      "end_time": 268130.0,
      "text": "So things like malaria, diarrhea."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 268130.0,
      "end_time": 270409.0,
      "text": "Coming up with new drugs and vaccines"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 270410.0,
      "end_time": 272540.0,
      "text": "and getting them out to all the kids in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 272540.0,
      "end_time": 274700.0,
      "text": "That's our main thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 274700.0,
      "end_time": 276360.0,
      "text": "Our second biggest thing is all in the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 276360.0,
      "end_time": 279530.0,
      "text": "which is trying to help improve the education system here."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 279530.0,
      "end_time": 280739.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 280740.0,
      "end_time": 283620.0,
      "text": "[APPLAUSE]"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 286300.0,
      "end_time": 287250.0,
      "text": "And how do you do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 287250.0,
      "end_time": 288930.0,
      "text": "I always think you get what you pay for."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 288930.0,
      "end_time": 292110.0,
      "text": "So if you don't pay teachers, because most teachers are"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 292110.0,
      "end_time": 295530.0,
      "text": "paying out of their own pocket to take care of these students."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 295530.0,
      "end_time": 298179.0,
      "text": "So how do you do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 298180.0,
      "end_time": 300730.0,
      "text": "Well, there are some really phenomenal teachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 300730.0,
      "end_time": 304800.0,
      "text": "And so the dream is that you could take that top 10%"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 304800.0,
      "end_time": 308789.0,
      "text": "and have them help the others to get best practices, the best"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 308790.0,
      "end_time": 312750.0,
      "text": "teaching ideas to spread all over the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 312750.0,
      "end_time": 316500.0,
      "text": "We're listening to you, obviously $40 billion"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 316500.0,
      "end_time": 317130.0,
      "text": "does a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 317130.0,
      "end_time": 319200.0,
      "text": "And there are other people that are helping."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 319200.0,
      "end_time": 321539.0,
      "text": "But what can we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 321540.0,
      "end_time": 325500.0,
      "text": "What is the best thing that you could say that just one"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 325500.0,
      "end_time": 326510.0,
      "text": "person can do to help?"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 326510.0,
      "end_time": 328830.0,
      "text": "Well particularly with schools, the ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 328830.0,
      "end_time": 331289.0,
      "text": "to go to the local public school or charter school"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 331290.0,
      "end_time": 334980.0,
      "text": "and engage with the kids, mentor kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 334980.0,
      "end_time": 336840.0,
      "text": "talk about the kind of work you do."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 336840.0,
      "end_time": 340200.0,
      "text": "There's huge opportunities there."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 340200.0,
      "end_time": 344205.0,
      "text": "With the challenges, say in Africa, part of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 344205.0,
      "end_time": 345840.0,
      "text": "is people's voice."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 345840.0,
      "end_time": 349200.0,
      "text": "There's a real question now whether the US takes"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 349200.0,
      "end_time": 353520.0,
      "text": "this less than 1% of our budget that saves tens of millions"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 353520.0,
      "end_time": 358229.0,
      "text": "of lives and whether we don't prioritize continuing that."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 358230.0,
      "end_time": 362340.0,
      "text": "So it's a hot debate in terms of is it good for America"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 362340.0,
      "end_time": 364739.0,
      "text": "to be generous and help the rest of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 364740.0,
      "end_time": 365970.0,
      "text": "live a healthy life."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 365970.0,
      "end_time": 369240.0,
      "text": "Well, I mean the fact that you're helping so many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 369240.0,
      "end_time": 370830.0,
      "text": "all around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 370830.0,
      "end_time": 373620.0,
      "text": "Because that, to me, is what when you have"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 373620.0,
      "end_time": 375780.0,
      "text": "that kind of money, it's for."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 375780.0,
      "end_time": 377880.0,
      "text": "That's the best thing you can do actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 377880.0,
      "end_time": 379920.0,
      "text": "You're making such a huge difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 379920.0,
      "end_time": 381212.0,
      "text": "I'm glad you're a billionaire."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 381212.0,
      "end_time": 385370.0,
      "text": "[APPLAUSE]"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 385370.0,
      "end_time": 388360.0,
      "text": "All right, you can learn more about the Bill and Melinda"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 388360.0,
      "end_time": 392730.0,
      "text": "Gates Foundation on the website and gatesletter.com."
    }
  ]
